### 1. 建立報名
POST http://localhost:3001/api/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "測試同學",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "phone": "0912345678"
}

### 1-2. 測試重複 Email (應該要失敗)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "分身帳號",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "phone": "0900000000"
}

### 2. 取得清單 (分頁測試)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/signup?page=1&limit=5

### 3. 更新資料 (請將下面的 ID 替換成剛剛 POST 回傳的 ID)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/signup/654321abcd...
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "confirmed",
  "phone": "0999888777"
}

### 4. 刪除資料
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/signup/654321abcd...
